{"tha-ap79:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap79:0.2":"Nagasamalavagga ","tha-ap79:0.3":"Sucidayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap79:1.1":"“Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap79:1.2":"sambuddho lokanayako; ","tha-ap79:1.3":"Sumedho nama namena, ","tha-ap79:1.4":"battimsavaralakkhano. ","tha-ap79:2.1":"Tassa kancanavannassa, ","tha-ap79:2.2":"dvipadindassa tadino; ","tha-ap79:2.3":"Panca suci maya dinna, ","tha-ap79:2.4":"sibbanatthaya civaram. ","tha-ap79:3.1":"Teneva sucidanena, ","tha-ap79:3.2":"nipunatthavipassakam; ","tha-ap79:3.3":"Tikkham lahunca phasunca, ","tha-ap79:3.4":"nanam me udapajjatha. ","tha-ap79:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap79:4.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap79:4.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","tha-ap79:4.4":"sammasambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap79:5.1":"Dvipadadhipati nama, ","tha-ap79:5.2":"rajano caturo ahum; ","tha-ap79:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap79:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap79:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap79:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap79:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap79:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sucidayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap79:8.1":"Sucidayakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}